Package: barcodeLabel
Title: Generate QR code and make PDF labels for printing
Version: 0.3.0
Authors: Junli Zhang <zhjl86@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Junli Zhang <zhjl86@gmail.com>
Description: A simple tools to generate QR codes (output is a matrix of 0 and 1). C codes were borrowed from the QR Code generator library (https://github.com/nayuki/QR-Code-generator). This package runs much faster than the  package qrcode (https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/qrcode/index.html). It now supports simple markdown text for mixed fontfaces in a line. For more complete rich text support, please check out "gridtext" package.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/pinbo/barcodeLabel
BugReports: https://github.com/pinbo/barcodeLabel/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
